  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a mixing bowl, combine the Canadian Cream Cheese, Heavy Cream, Sugar, and Vanilla Extract. Mix until fully combined.",
    "Add in the Rolled Oats and Flour, stirring continuously until well incorporated.",
    "Transfer the mixture into an oven-safe dish or tin pan. Press down firmly to form a solid layer on top of your dessert or whatever you're serving it with.",
    "Bake for 12-15 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool slightly before serving."
